s/puyo_anim_g-Steam-BG.jpg?t=1718358784\" /> <strong>Versus</strong> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/546050/extras/Green.jpg?t=1718358784\" /><br>Players compete head-to-head in either Puyo Puyo or Tetris to fight in the puzzle battle of their lives.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/546050/extras/Blue.jpg?t=1718358784\" /> <strong>Swap</strong> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/546050/extras/puyo_anim_b-Steam-BG.jpg?t=1718358784\" /><br>Players' abilities are put to the ultimate test when they compete on both Puyo Puyo and Tetris boards, which switch back and forth at set intervals.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/546050/extras/puyo_anim_p-Steam-BG.jpg?t=1718358784\" /> <strong>Fusion</strong> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/546050/extras/Purple.jpg?t=1718358784\" /><br>A true hybrid game where players compete with Puyos and Tetriminos together on the same board, requiring deft, on-the-fly thinking to become victorious.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/546050/extras/Red.jpg?t=1718358784\" /> <strong>Big Bang</strong> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/546050/extras/puyo_anim_r-Steam-BG.jpg?t=1718358784\" /><br>It's a race to the finish as players compete against each other to clear unique challenge boards as quickly as possible to win.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/546050/extras/puyo_anim_y-Steam-BG.jpg?t=1718358784\" /> <strong>Party</strong> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/546050/extra